PRICE REDUCED !!!
ASSUMABLE FHA LOAN FOR ANY BUYER WHO QUALIFIES. LOW- LOW RATE OF 2.625% WITH A FIRST LOAN OF $229,500.00. Welcome to this exquisite 2019-built single-story home in a gated community. With 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 1,661 sq ft of living space, this turnkey property features a spacious Great Room, a well-appointed Kitchen with gas stove/range, a walk-in Pantry. Laundry Room, and a covered patio. Upgrades include premium lighting, a dedicated garage breaker, and pre-installed solar system hooks for energy efficiency. Your pets will adore the convenient Doggy Door. Kitchen and bathrooms both upgraded stainless features. The Master Bedroom offers a stylish end-suite.
